id: pm-qbts
title: Accept positional title for pm plan create like pm create does
description: "Inconsistency: `pm create 'my task'` accepts positional title (pm-7vm9 session 11), but `pm plan create 'my plan'` requires `--title` flag. Agents waste tokens on retry guidance after picking up the create pattern. Add positional [title] argument to `pm plan create` subcommand and inject hint into requireStringOption when missing."
type: Task
status: closed
priority: 2
