author: claude-code-agent
acceptance_criteria: `pm plan create 'foo'` works; help shows positional; regression added in plan-command.spec.ts
parent: pm-rnpb
resolution: Added positional-title handling for pm plan create when --title is omitted.
expected_result: pm plan create 'title' succeeds and creates a Plan with that title while non-create subcommands still treat the argument as an id.
actual_result: CLI integration and release gates verified positional plan create works with expected title and scope.
